OL,3,C'She was so frightened': Mum gives
OL,4,Cevidence in alleged rape trial of teen
OL,5,Cboys
OL,7,FThe mother of a teenage girl who was
OL,8,Fallegedly raped by three young boys
OL,9,Fhas told a jury her daughter "was so
OL,10,Ffrightened."
OL,12,FManchester's Minshull Street Crown
OL,13,FCourt heard the three boys, then aged
OL,14,F12, 13, and 14, allegedly "took it in
OL,15,Fturns" to rape the then 13-year-old
OL,16,Fgirl in bushes close to the Newbold
OL,17,FTram Stop in Rochdale in February 2024.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/7
