OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F398A1773061886
OL,3,C'She was so frightened': Mum gives
OL,4,Cevidence in alleged rape trial of teen
OL,5,Cboys
OL,7,FThe three boys, who cannot be named
OL,8,Fbecause of their ages, deny the
OL,9,Fcharges they face. Two, now aged 15
OL,10,Fand 16, are standing trial. The third,
OL,11,Fwho was aged 12 at the time and is now
OL,12,F14, has been deemed unfit to stand
OL,13,Ftrial.
OL,15,FThe alleged victim also cannot be
OL,16,Fnamed.
OL,18,FOn Friday 6 March, the girl's mother
OL,19,Fgave evidence from the witness box,
OL,20,Fand described the moment she was told
OL,21,Fabout the alleged incident.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/7
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
