PN,39803
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F398A1773061886
OL,3,C'She was so frightened': Mum gives
OL,4,Cevidence in alleged rape trial of teen
OL,5,Cboys
OL,7,FShe told jurors she saw her phone
OL,8,Fflash, but ignored it because she was
OL,9,Fdriving.
OL,11,FThe mother answered when it rang again.
OL,13,FProsecutor Kim Whittlestone asked:
OL,14,F"What did you hear?"
OL,16,F"Distress," she answered.
OL,18,FShe told the jury she heard a family
OL,19,Fmember "screaming" and saying "What?
OL,20,FWhat? What's happened?"
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/7
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,399,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39804
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F398A1773061886
OL,3,C'She was so frightened': Mum gives
OL,4,Cevidence in alleged rape trial of teen
OL,5,Cboys
OL,7,FThe mother told the court: "Then
OL,8,F(they) said the words no mum ever
OL,9,Fwants to hear - (she) has been raped."
OL,11,FCrying, the woman told jurors: "I
OL,12,Fstopped the car in the middle of the
OL,13,Froad. Everything was a blur. I
OL,14,Fcouldn't drive, I couldn't function."
OL,16,FShe said she "screamed and shouted" at
OL,17,Fthe family member to "go to her"
OL,18,Fdaughter. "I don't remember any of the
OL,19,Fcalls" she added.
OL,26,@pD@ApmpD@FpnqD@QpmqD@Upn
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/7
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
