CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F398A1773061886
OL,3,C'She was so frightened': Mum gives
OL,4,Cevidence in alleged rape trial of teen
OL,5,Cboys
OL,7,FThe woman told jurors that when she
OL,8,Farrived at the scene, her daughter and
OL,9,Fher friend were sat in a family
OL,10,Fmember's vehicle as they waited for
OL,11,Fthe police.
OL,13,FShe said her daughter told her: "Mum,
OL,14,Fthey've done it to my bum and they
OL,15,Fhurt my bum.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/7
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
