PN,39806
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F398A1773061886
OL,3,C'She was so frightened': Mum gives
OL,4,Cevidence in alleged rape trial of teen
OL,5,Cboys
OL,7,F"She was so frightened, so distressed.
OL,8,FThe only thing I said to her was 'are
OL,9,Fyou bleeding? We need to go to
OL,10,Fhospital'. The police came and took
OL,11,Fher to the hospital. I didn't leave
OL,12,F(her) side."
OL,14,FJurors were also shown a ten second
OL,15,Fvideo of the alleged attack, which
OL,16,Fproseutors say was filmed on the 16-
OL,17,Fyear-old's mobile phone.
OL,19,FThe video was played through twice at
OL,20,Ffull speed and once slowed down. The
OL,21,Fjury could hear laughing in the clip.
OL,26,@tD@ApmtD@Epn
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/7
