OL,3,C'She was so frightened': Mum gives
OL,4,Cevidence in alleged rape trial of teen
OL,5,Cboys
OL,7,FThe footage was later "circulated
OL,8,Famongst themselves" and "others",
OL,9,Fprosecutors earlier said.
OL,11,FThe trial continues.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/7
